headline: JANA PARTNERS, TRAVIS KELCE, AND LEADING EXECUTIVES INVEST IN SIX FLAGS ENTERTAINMENT
summary: JANA Partners ("JANA") today announced that it has partnered with Super Bowl Champion Travis Kelce as well as consumer executive Glenn Murphy and technology executive Dave Habiger, (the "Group") in an investment in Six Flags Entertainment Corporation (NYSE: FUN) ("Six Flags" or the "Company"). The Group collectively owns an economic interest of approximately 9%.

headline: Lululemon (LULU) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of athletic apparel retailer Lululemon (NASDAQ:LULU) jumped 5.5% in the afternoon session after the stock's positive momentum continued as BNP Paribas Exane upgraded its rating from underperform to neutral.
